            "body": "That will be helpful, +1 for the propose too!.\n\nI think we can make it compatible with syntax in YARN-3028, and in addition, do you think is it possible we can add labels appeared in the conf file to clusterNodeLabels automatically? Which we can make the config file simpler.",
